                    <h4>Some immunologists directed their researches on the antibodies structure and the immune system:</h4>

                    <p>In 1972, Professor Rodney Porter received the Nobel Prize for his discovery about the chemical structure of antibodies. Also in 1972, Professor Gerald Edelman received the Nobel Prize in medecine for his researches on the immune system.</p>
